<topic id='element_nhs_continuing_healthcare_referrals_concluded__within_28_days_standard_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: NHS CONTINUING HEALTHCARE REFERRALS CONCLUDED (WITHIN 28 DAYS STANDARD) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_nhs_continuing_healthcare_referrals_concluded__within_28_days_standard_">NHS CONTINUING HEALTHCARE REFERRALS CONCLUDED (WITHIN 28 DAYS STANDARD)</xref>
 is the number of referrals for 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
 that were concluded within 28 days.        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
The 28 days referral time starts from the earliest notification to the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">CCG</xref>), or 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 acting on behalf of the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>, that full consideration for 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 is required                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
The referral time ends on the date the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>
 makes a verified decision on 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
 eligibility or the referral is discounted: 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_nhs_continuing_healthcare_referrals__discounted_before_assessment_">NHS CONTINUING HEALTHCARE REFERRALS (DISCOUNTED BEFORE ASSESSMENT)</xref>
 where the 
                                <xref outputclass="attribute"
                        keyref="attribute_nhs_continuing_healthcare_type">NHS CONTINUING HEALTHCARE TYPE</xref>
 is National Code 
                                <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                           keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>'</i>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
</body>
